Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:10.00,英语字幕,,0,0,0,,歌手：Gotye ft & Kimbra
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.97,0:00:23.50,英语字幕,,0,0,0,,Now and then I think of when we were together\N{\fn楷体_gb2312\fs28\c&H00E3E749}偶尔想起那一起的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.59,0:00:30.72,英语字幕,,0,0,0,,Like when you said you felt so happy you could die\N{\fn楷体_gb2312\fs28\c&H00E3E749}仿佛还是你快乐至极的时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.75,0:00:36.64,英语字幕,,0,0,0,,Told myself that you were right for me\N{\fn楷体_gb2312\fs28\c&H00E3E749}告诉自己 你就是我想要的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.31,0:00:40.11,英语字幕,,0,0,0,,But felt so lonely in your company\N{\fn楷体_gb2312\fs28\c&H00E3E749}可是有了你的陪伴 并没有减少我的孤单
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.10,0:00:44.97,英语字幕,,0,0,0,,But that was love and it's an ache I still remember\N{\fn楷体_gb2312\fs28\c&H00E3E749}那就是爱 就是那忘不掉的疼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.12,0:01:07.35,英语字幕,,0,0,0,,You can get addicted to a certain kind of sadness\N{\fn楷体_gb2312\fs28\c&H00E3E749}对于某个伤痛都会沉迷的你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.15,0:01:12.65,英语字幕,,0,0,0,,Like resignation to the end\N{\fn楷体_gb2312\fs28\c&H00E3E749}最后却好像无可奈何
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.06,0:01:14.99,英语字幕,,0,0,0,,Always the end\N{\fn楷体_gb2312\fs28\c&H00E3E749}总是这样到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.32,0:01:21.51,英语字幕,,0,0,0,,So when we found that we could not make sense\N{\fn楷体_gb2312\fs28\c&H00E3E749}所以当我们感情也平淡的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.78,0:01:24.74,英语字幕,,0,0,0,,Well you said that we would still be friends\N{\fn楷体_gb2312\fs28\c&H00E3E749}你会说我们还是朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.53,0:01:30.40,英语字幕,,0,0,0,,But I'll admit that I was glad that it was over\N{\fn楷体_gb2312\fs28\c&H00E3E749}我承认我愿意结束这样的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.94,0:01:35.57,英语字幕,,0,0,0,,But you didn't have to cut me off\N{\fn楷体_gb2312\fs28\c&H00E3E749}可是你不必这样远离我
